{"tid":806524,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"你地用開邊個出糧戶口？求推介","createTime":"2018-09-04T17:36:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-11T10:35:47.000Z","uid":78377,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"177e03297b3e55329005b3d47ccabde311870231","tid":806524,"uid":78377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T17:36:18.000Z","msg":"要開個出糧戶口<br />\n糾結緊 citi, sc 定 大新<br />\n<br />\nciti個月月增息好似幾吸引 問題係我打算月供股票<br />\n我應該唔會每個月有8000蚊放入銀行<br />\n但係座底會有0.12%活期息(？)<br />\n<br />\nsc就可以直接食300蚊迎新<br />\n而活期息1%個優惠得6個月<br />\n<br />\n大新我見好多人都推 <br />\n但係我唔係好識玩 <br />\n佢果個360戶口好似要放好大舊錢入去先有高息<br />\n定係開其他戶口都有高少少既活期息？<br />\n<br />\nbtw 仲有citi 同 大新[轉帳易] 可以免費本地跨銀行轉帳 都有credit<br />\n<br />\n唔知應該點揀..."},{"pid":"84048204323e591b077c85eef1efa8be8b54eb87","tid":806524,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T18:04:42.000Z","msg":"hsbc"},{"pid":"fe16ebbb4e4fa4d7c09dacdb7c5be952933a4f58","tid":806524,"uid":42314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T18:15:14.000Z","msg":"是但啦"},{"pid":"a6accbdd6fa5e29f139ca431fd48cb36701f6d4e","tid":806524,"uid":78377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T06:52:08.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"b7af7bc7453edc0834c546e48bb75772c6900675","tid":806524,"uid":68097,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T06:55:35.000Z","msg":"都係一撚樣"},{"pid":"acd8e25f9646c6d3b3eb0d268c0102eef7453e08","tid":806524,"uid":203619,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T07:05:06.000Z","msg":"覺得邊張卡靚咪邊張囉"},{"pid":"2cd7310c90860c7749a37150dc7bcc13553462f7","tid":806524,"uid":143241,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T07:06:42.000Z","msg":"邊間都好,一定唔好用中銀"},{"pid":"4c7ad3065e73592ff9f5e72474369e9f07a4dccd","tid":806524,"uid":78377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7af7bc7453edc0834c546e48bb75772c6900675","tid":806524,"uid":68097,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"rep